                    <h1 class="domdom">01</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/409">Kiss Me Kate (1953)</a></h1>

                    <h2>1 Nov 2009, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>"The Greatest of all Great MGM Musicals!" Shakespeare's The Taming of the Shrew meets Cole Porter in this play within a musical within a film. Originally filmed in 3D - expect a surfeit of objects thrown at the camera as well as classic ditties 'So In Love', 'Too Darn Hot' and (in canny preparation for next week's festival of the same name!) 'Wunderbar'. Keep your eyes peeled for the Bob Fosse cameo.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/409">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

