                    <h1 class="domdom">10</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/395">Les Demoiselles De Rochefort (1967)</a></h1>

                    <h2>10 Jan 2010, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Agnes Varda and Jacques Demy collaborate directing the charming Catherine Deneuve and Gene Kelly. Its a companion piece to The Umbrellas of Cherbourg 1964 using the same magical combination of a Michel Legrand score, immaculate kitsch art direction and a romantic story line to make the heart sing too.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/395">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

