                    <h1 class="domdom">05</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/593">Fame (1980)</a></h1>

                    <h2>5 Sep 2010, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>We sashay into the questionable world of 80s musicals with this tale of unadulterated, grabbing ambition. Come and remember the leg warmers, remember the routines, remember the songs and, most importantly, remember&hellip;my name. Because if they've really got what it takes, it's going to take everything they've got.</p>

                    <p class="viewlink"><a href="/on/film/593">Read More &raquo;</a></p>

