                    <h1 class="domdom">09</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/733">Top Hat (1935)</a></h1>

                    <h2>9 Dec 2010, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>For the last Decades of Musicals film we are throwing chronology to the wind and going back to the 1930s where, let's be honest, all the best musicals live. Astaire and Rogers partner up again and croon such classics as 'Cheek to Cheek' and, of course, 'Top Hat&hellip;'.</p>

